Filmmaker Aditya Chopra’s much-anticipated directorial comeback “Befikre”, starring Ranveer Singh and Vaani Kapoor, will hit theatres on December 9 this year.Ranveer and Vaani shared the release date of the romance in a short video shared on Youtube. The actress first revealed the date in French, which the “Bajirao Mastani” star then translates in Hindi.The film will be shot in Paris, France.Aditya announced his return to direction with “Befikre - Those Who Dare To Love” on his father Yash Chopra’s 83rd birth anniversary last year.Aditya last directed Shah Rukh Khan-Anushka Sharma starrer “Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi” in 2008.Check the video here: